name: receiverCode
description: The CBP assigned code for the ‘data processing’ site/location of the transmitter (i.e., both sender of the batch and recipient of the response).

name: senderCode
description: Transmitter’s identification code (as assigned by CBP).

name: communicationPassword
description: Space fill. A pre-established password used to authorize the transmitter of the data.

name: transmissionDate
description: Transmitter’s date of batch transmission. Space fill if not used.

name: officeCode
description: A code agreed upon by the transmitter and CBP representing a specific ‘office’ (or sub-location).
